msgid "The standard music enabled by default. It has a Eurobeat flavor that pumps you up in a race."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4693	DESC"
msgid "A manly rock number. I love singing it at karaoke... Occasionally..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4762	DESC"
msgid "A high-tempo dance track. It was a big hit back in the day. Haruka used to sing it all the time."
msgstr ""

